last resort.
SHEPPARD
All right, spare me the history lessons.
TODD
A terminally ill Wraith...could...occasionally ...restore himself to
perfect health...if he allowed an Iratus..."bug", as you call them,
specifically a queen, to feed on him.
KELLER
And you're just bringing this up now?
TODD
(speaking with difficulty)
The process was abandoned long ago because it is dangerous, almost
always resulting in the death of the Wraith in question. I
only...consider it now because...it would appear that we
are...beyond...hope. Now there is...a planet less than three days
